/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed36df367cbe3c84bf16ca8fe08b5042c639ae2d","tid":290951,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"#235珀* &bull; 3h<br />\n<blockquote>讀藝術嘅人會好明白呢種感覺<br />\n有時真係會比人inspired<br />\n但係會盡量唔抄得咁足 最多都係攞少少做元素<br />\n屌你樓主呢句直頭中心句啦<br />\n時間又咁近<br />\n直copy中心句喎大佬 <br />\nphrase 都廢是re喎佢<br />\n屌佢死基佬 係唔鐘意佢架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nexactly<br />\n<br />\n我最覺得佢抄，就係因為成句中心句出左黎<br />\n就算係idea似，會唔會咁岩真係評審完就出一篇野，仲要hashtag正正就係句中心句?<br />\n<br />\n多謝你明白我"},{"pid":"ec4d7e9f8838c3c71f6b1cd14bd42cab49cf135e","tid":290951,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:54:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cf493137ba82824be87d265e5ecc5b975c81644","tid":290951,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"手足阿古路係咪有入咩90後廢青集中益 見到有條友叫阿古路 唔知是咪你來"},{"pid":"00e5c9f7e287e5ccf3d3d947b37b42a9d3c9484a","tid":290951,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/p43YeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fp43YeV.jpg&h=95f84457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來炒車位絲打好撚正，吾笑了</blockquote><br />\nig?</blockquote><br />\n吾好再笑了</blockquote><br />\n想安慰絲打"},{"pid":"ae1872b0cb23e585e2511f61d3e5193daa528312","tid":290951,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:55:40.000Z","msg":"幸福係由社會定義架on9<br />\n<br />\n有錢有地位有權力就係幸福啦"},{"pid":"9bcef8508b9dd33a9a192a277faa4993a1056229","tid":290951,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/p43YeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fp43YeV